('79ec9c6b-182c-4485-a26b-676d1dceeb6c', 'admin', '2019-06-09 14:31', 1, '\r\n== Step 1 == \r\n{{/IP7XDqZ4v1E_HyTB6guf6gZqgKqeqJ3F8A.png|}}\r\n === Enter the <em>Invoices </em>menu in the <em>Accounts Receivable</em> tab. === \r\n----\r\n== Step 2 == \r\n{{/BtzfuqagZdQ1CHv4M7aReXiKkM3RzCSDgA.png|}}\r\n === Select the batch of invoices you would like to edit the description for, and click <em>Edit</em>. === \r\n----\r\n== Step 3 == \r\n{{/akcaezYABp3F9yswkJI6Sjr8NJWSZA7J_A.png|}}\r\nSelect the expense item and click <em>Edit.</em>\r\n----\r\n== Step 4 == \r\n{{/Wc2nN6FQXwQ7KgZ3paqvkhJUBoQ8iqUlqw.png|}}\r\n === Enter the Description you would like to appear in Levy.  === \r\n === Click the <em>Save </em>icon at the bottom of the page. === \r\n === Click the <em>Save </em>button on the left hand menu.  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 5 == \r\n{{/wD7PArYqqucjH8gsvUT0T3YDc7s2SllTfA.png|}}\r\n === Any changes made will be applied to ALL invoices within the selected batch.  === \r\n----\r\n', @liid);
