('69d5be56-5947-40da-bfb8-a6aff24853a9', 'admin', '2019-06-09 14:31', 1, '\r\n== Step 1 == \r\n{{/k47xdJbztwhxG2IKsREx8T1XB3OjDNfm-A.png|}}\r\n === Enter the <em>Unit Plan</em> menu. === \r\n----\r\n== Step 2 == \r\n{{/cYvsfmBtzwopH3C3BtDpqJW74gHC94ACNQ.png|}}\r\n === Enter the <em>Reports </em>menu === \r\n----\r\n== Step 3 == \r\n{{/HTjHCBX0eAAezHVDbAIi3FPt-cjTECfg3g.png|}}\r\n === \r\n === \r\n === Tick the<em> Proprietor Statement Report</em> checkbox. === \r\n === Select the proprietor you would like to generate a statement for. === \r\n === Select the period you would like to generate the statement for. === \r\n === Click OK to generate the statement.  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 4 == \r\n== {{/7X9XhFym-lsl23muIV_aLYjy2x8xLbSFtg.png|}} ==  === \r\n === \r\n === The statement will be downloaded onto your computer. === \r\n----\r\n', @liid);
