('224afb61-98a9-470a-8888-6c5b654e942a', 'admin', '2019-06-09 14:31', 1, '<span style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;"><strong >Step 1:</span>\r\n<span style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;"><strong >{{/8Kfo-dq-bpA7WdX3VWZRK5U_uDKEel9m-w.png|}}</span>\r\n<span style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Enter the <em>Levies </em>menu from the home page.</span>\r\n<span style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"></span>\r\n----\r\n== Step 2: == \r\n== {{/9XKbDKiS-Bo-mdjrRI9x4lPnhzihd8Nh1Q.png|}} == \r\n === Select the <em>Begin </em>and <em>End </em>date for the levy. === \r\n==  == \r\n----\r\n== Step 3: == \r\n{{/TvcOkCPdJolF3l7MDadak2vdnKK_2wkinA.png|}}\r\n === Select <em>Budget Levy.</em> === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 4: == \r\n{{/9I083r5z4X8UyP0DT3G0NfkvLBF4FhST7A.png|}}\r\n === Select <em>All </em>for all budget items, or <em>Expenses </em>for expense budgeted items only. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n === <em> </em>\r\n== Step 5: ===  == {{/JsRTgJfdoTtjEFNB-kl--lU77Ze716rHrg.png|}}\r\n === Select <em>Add New Row </em>to add additional budget items. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n<span style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;">Step 6:</span>\r\n{{/SElb7Tfi-MkuL2Kvgz8PGVFLb_RvFzy6Ug.png|}}\r\n === Enter information on the budget item.  === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 7: == \r\n{{/DPpa6aB5m-8Dx6LagM8qXHDaVVMdd7enoA.png|}}\r\n === Click on the <em>Save </em>icon at the bottom of the page to save budget item. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  === \r\n== Step 8: == \r\n== {{/-5zS1gj3Mr4XhTo9XG7ksJ0brgyHvnXzSQ.png|}} == \r\n === Select <em>Next Step.</em> === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  === \r\n==  == \r\n== Step 9: == \r\n==  == {{/2gkAsU0-qT8AmzgbVMHZs5XTsfkU6nttXg.png|}}\r\n === Enter the number of <em>Instalments </em>and the <em>Dates</em> for each <em>Instalment. </em>Click <em>Default Description </em>and <em>OK.</em> === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  === \r\n==  == \r\n== Step 10: == \r\n== {{/WaHb6pK1-ofVZ-v1VUrrOQxokRemBVp04Q.png|}} ==  === Enter <em>Billing Date, Due Date, </em>and <em>Apply Date. Apply Date </em>is the same as <em>Billing Date.</em> === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 11: == \r\n== {{/zL0r3ULiM1BPkC9ujMlMMybHDN91WhlUfw.png|}} ==  ===  === {{/S5EnAl3eajnfYRlXNpsA4EvHrB9hOIUwCg.png|}}\r\n === Tick Box and select <em>Fill </em>to evenly divide the budget total into each instalment. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  \r\n== Step 12: ===  == \r\n{{/O9BtZ7j-rVNhOLs21v81su80ekRgvw1how.png|}}\r\n === Select <em>Submit </em>to save levy/invoice.  === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  === \r\n ===  === \r\n==  == \r\n==  == <span style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"></span>\r\n', @liid);
