('a001cbdf-0fcc-4736-843b-a5199d1cadc8', 'admin', '2019-06-09 14:31', 1, '\r\n== Step 1: == \r\n== {{/LOeNVXZ72PuN36xaCXVO7aTxsOTh-ZqwaA.png|}} ==  === Enter the <em>Debtors </em>menu from the Uxtrata home page. === \r\n ===  === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 2: == \r\n{{/6QVt2hk6oSVQDXbzKShgQ421zp1DNG0E5w.png|}}\r\n === Select <em>Add.</em> === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 3: == \r\n== {{/VLMkLzWuTQbzrHBNKq9oQYWcpDL7xQF8vQ.png|}} == \r\n ===  ===  ===  ===  ===  === \r\n<ul>\n<li>\r\n === Enter the <em>Name </em>of the debtor. === </li>\n<li>\r\n === Select the <em>Type, Payment Term, Payment Type.</em> === </li>\n<li>\r\n\n ===  ===  === Enter <em>Salutation</em>- how they are addressed in written communication created by Uxtrata. === \n</li>\n<li>\r\n\n ===  ===  === Tick <em>Print</em> or <em>Email </em>in regards to the way that want to receive documents. === \n</li>\n</ul> ===  === \r\n === Note: <em>Email </em>needs to be ticked for debtor to receive email correspondence. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 4: == \r\n== {{/oOWJc_Y39UV9yv6GUi-WftI97hYSLTPdjA.png|}} == \r\n === Select <em>Save </em>to confirm. === \r\n==  == \r\n==  == \r\n', @liid);
