('0a426765-52a2-47a9-af0e-ce79e1866e55', 'admin', '2019-06-09 14:31', 1, '\r\n== Step 1: == \r\n{{/W7iIlxXC3fHbBbXj3Aqiuz0C4Wi5y_IrhA.png|}}\r\n === Enter the <em>Budget </em>menu from the home page. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  === \r\n== Step 2: == \r\n{{/IQ-JT59CiqobqGIW2MWbqIMlh4eWQRWyfQ.png|}}\r\n<span style="font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Select the S<em>tart Date</em> for the budget</span>\r\n----\r\n== Step 3: == \r\n{{/UYHYQHWpRuYaCaYHHoEGpgpwvfywMjb2mQ.png|}}\r\n === Click on <em>Add New Row</em> to create a new expense item. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 4: == \r\n== {{/3XT8mp-_EqzclSHjGfdHzY7n8blpmDx8JA.png|}} ==  === Select <em>Budget Name </em>and <em>Scale.</em> === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 5: == \r\n== {{/hUVXfz4uH7m7yJqNfDCPUVTVo4ZyWOWWuw.png|}} == \r\n== {{/eAA5kCPQXdhxQysrknLwtUp6NzE8vFlmfA.png|}} ==  === Click on <em>Fill </em>and enter value to fill each of the 12 months with the same value.  === \r\n ===  === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  ===  \r\n== Step 6: == \r\n== {{/nvNiYFP4zgz7YSyoQFAzw5HXkTsl6bEXFA.png|}}{{/uPHLnGfjdRnEoWDE3F5w_HAsbsixBVnkVg.png|}} == \r\n==  ==  === Click on <em>Split</em><em> </em>and enter <em>Total Amount</em><em> </em> to be evenly distributed into each month. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 7: == \r\n{{/kHR37QSk0WLYUgS31tGIjREpSItEdBi52Q.png|}}\r\n === Click on the <em>Save icon </em>on the bottom of the page to save budget row === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 8: == \r\n== {{/ELgjQYWHPgBLpJeYYd_DcxFPerZ9JmtyzQ.png|}} == \r\n === Click on Save<em> </em>to confirm budget item === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n ===  === \r\n==  == \r\n==  == \r\n==  == \r\n', @liid);
