('d9de19a2-4603-4014-8cf5-71f53a7913e5', 'admin', '2019-06-09 14:31', 1, '\r\n== Step 1: == \r\n== {{/Ww7AiJxTBWsDjKUfRJIgro-z0RgV-YJK0Q.png|}} == \r\n === Click on <em>Portal Drive</em>. === \r\n<span style="font-family: Helvetica,sans-serif;"> === Note: If you do not have one, please contact support@uxtrata.com === </span>\r\n<span style="font-family: Helvetica,sans-serif;"> ===  === </span>\r\n----\r\n ===  === \r\n== Step 2: == \r\n== {{/efnfZnUQd7NjB-r4tNNzDdXPtqBtZpPOLg.png|}} == \r\n === Select the body corporate that you want to work on. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 3: == \r\n== {{/j_PrqpD9iGFCqvXUFJjPeDxezc2jevTg5A.png|}} == \r\n === Select folder  === \r\n<ul>\n<li>\r\n === Individual unit folder (1A, 1B, 1C etc. these files can only be seen by unit owners) === </li>\n<li>\r\n === Committee folder (these files can only be seen by body corporate committee members). === </li>\n<li>\r\n === Common folders (these can be viewed by all unit owners).  === </li>\n</ul> ===  === \r\n === {{/YzygVpVfSJeWDNA8WWXd4dxRYZ0RzbscUw.png|}} === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 4: == \r\n ===  ===  === Drag and drop files into the folders accordingly. === \r\n ===  === \r\n ===  === \r\n==  == \r\n==  == \r\n', @liid);
