('15ef4e9d-b866-46a5-91f9-acbbaa2a174a', 'admin', '2019-06-09 14:31', 1, '\r\n== Step 1: == \r\n{{/F9XF7l19MlwOl17Khj_thLfGvNYFZ3zvaA.png|}}\r\n === Select <em>Financial Reports </em>from the home page. === \r\n----\r\n== Step 2: == \r\n{{/waCHAJWjUxKsKszM1OAo4MmIMtEpzBTKKg.png|}}\r\n<ul>\n<li>\r\n === Select the <em>Period </em>for the financial report that you want to create. === </li>\n<li>\r\n === Select the <em>Year Begin </em>date, this is the start of the financial period for this body corporate. === </li>\n<li>\r\n === <em>Start Page Num </em>is the page number of the first page of the report you wish to create. === </li>\n</ul> ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 3: == \r\n== {{/kl_4_kAd__ZvU7Hby7GSjHNLG5TERda4Qg.png|}} ==  === Select the report that you wish to generate. === \r\n ===  === \r\n----\r\n== Step 4: == \r\n== {{/_HRZGN_C5Sfgf7rVgIYHa2Oag7vOLb1UTQ.png|}} ==  ===  ===  === You can select: === \r\n<ol>\n<li>\r\n === <em>Print</em>- the report will be opened in a new tab in the browser, select print or save as you wish. (Please ensure popups have not been blocked on your browser). === </li>\n<li>\r\n === <em>Export PDF</em>- the report will be saved as a PDF file onto your computer. === </li>\n</ol> ===  ===  ===  === \r\n', @liid);
